{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As the library prepares for Swift 6 we are in the process of updating the library’s APIs for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sendability and isolation where appropriate, and doing so in a backwards compatible way. Prior"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to version 1.14 of the library the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store"},{"type":"text","text":" type has only ever been meant to be used on the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"main thread, but that contract was not enforced in any major way. If a store was interacted with"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on a background thread a runtime warning would be emitted, but the compiler had no knowledge of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the type’s isolation."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"That now changes in 1.14 where "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store"},{"type":"text","text":" is now officially "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"type":"text","text":"-isolated. This has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"done in a way that should be 100% backwards compatible, and if you have problems please open a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"http:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-composable-architecture\/discussions"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"However, if you are using "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"strict"}]},{"type":"text","text":" concurrency settings in your app, then there is one circumstance"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in which you may have a compilation error. If you are accessing the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"store"},{"type":"text","text":" in a view method or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property in Xcode <16, then you may have to mark that property as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"diff","code":[" struct FeatureView: View {","   let store: StoreOf<Feature>"," ","   var body: some View {","     \/\/ ...","   }"," ","+  @MainActor","   var title: some View {","     Text(store.name)","   }"," }"]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.14"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store"},{"type":"text","text":" type is now officially "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"type":"text","text":" isolated."}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Migrating to 1.14","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture"]]},"references":{"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture/Store":{"role":"symbol","title":"Store","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Store"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A store represents the runtime that powers the application. It is the object that you will pass"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"around to views that need to interact with the application."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Store"}],"url":"\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/store"},"http://github.com/pointfreeco/swift-composable-architecture/discussions":{"title":"discussion","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"discussion"}],"type":"link","identifier":"http:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-composable-architecture\/discussions","url":"http:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-composable-architecture\/discussions"},"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture":{"role":"collection","title":"ComposableArchitecture","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Composable Architecture (TCA, for short) is a library for building applications in a consistent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and understandable way, with composition, testing, and ergonomics in mind. It can be used in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI, UIKit, and more, and on any Apple platform (iOS, macOS, tvOS, and watchOS)."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/composablearchitecture"}}}